headline: MSCI Q3 Deep Dive: Index Strength, AI Progress and Private Markets Shape Outlook
summary: Investment analytics provider MSCI (NYSE:MSCI) met Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q3 CY2025, with sales up 9.5% year on year to $793.4 million. Its non-GAAP profit of $4.47 per share was 2.3% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
